Hi, you can use `Switch` in addition to `When` , for example:
```Switch(\.$someString) {
    Case("a") {
        Summary("a")
    }
    Case("b") {
        Summary("b")
    }
    Case(["c", "d"]) {
        Summary("c or d")
    }
    DefaultCase {
        Summary("Default")
    }
}```

